metadata.name: Moment of Bliss
metadata.description:
The world is full of disturbance where will peace be found on the ground ?
The sky has invited you to swing under the cloud now make the sky your home and companion to the moon
just forget everything and enjoy the moment of bliss

in this surreal art the lady is swinging in the sky away from her daily disturbance at peace of her mind free from all the worries 

Artwork created using Photoshop 
dimension 3200x4000
